WEBVTT

00:00:54.124 --> 00:01:00.008
And then, learning that just about
100 percent of climate scientists agree.

00:01:00.032 --> 00:01:04.984
They agree that a drastic
emergency is upon us,

00:01:05.008 --> 00:01:08.058
that it is human-caused.

00:01:10.450 --> 00:01:11.606
But they said

00:01:11.630 --> 00:01:13.684
we can do something about it.

00:01:13.708 --> 00:01:16.919
We have the time, the technology,

00:01:16.943 --> 00:01:18.165
the tools.

00:01:18.189 --> 00:01:21.430
We have everything we need
except political will

00:01:21.454 --> 00:01:22.608
to meet the challenge,

00:01:22.632 --> 00:01:24.615
and it's an enormous challenge.

00:01:25.879 --> 00:01:29.991
We have 11 years, many say, a decade,